{
  "id": "absorb_substance",
  "category": "mass_transfer",
  "description": "Selectively absorbs substances from environment (water, soil, food, toxins). Enables nutrient uptake, toxin sequestration, and chemical-based metabolism. Low baseline cost; selectivity tunes efficacy.",
